This directory contains the challenge evaluation framework for AI Goat:

  • engine.py — dynamic per-user flag generation and verification
  • evaluator.py — base evaluator interface and shared context
  • registry.py — evaluator discovery and lookup
  • evaluators/ — 9 exploit evaluators encoding attack detection logic,
    pattern matching rules, and success thresholds for each challenge

The evaluators define what constitutes a successful exploit in each
challenge. They encode specific attack patterns, detection thresholds,
secret markers, and multi-turn analysis logic that represent the
training methodology of the AI Goat platform.

